{"tid":689642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"咱們咱你老母臭西","createTime":"2018-06-04T08:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:38:51.000Z","uid":168808,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91b825d87e7da8f49f8322e8eb95f67b895287db","tid":689642,"uid":168808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"小弟海外撚<br />\n近排回港 見到班朋友 (2X歲)<br />\n傾傾下計 佢地無啦啦講左句 咱(喒)們一陣去邊食飯<br />\n我當堂嚇左跳 大屌左佢一獲 話佢用蝗語唔撚係掛<br />\n佢地屌返我轉頭話講下笑 洗唔洗咁認真<br />\n首先 點解扮大陸狗係會覺得係好笑<br />\n唔覺得有失身分 眨低自己<br />\n潛移默化呢啲野真係好恐怖<br />\n個個都貪得意用蝗語 就會變潮流<br />\n到時真係諗定移民<br />\n我宜家諗緊同唔同班撚樣絕交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 絕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 樓主on99唔撚update 香港一早己經變香港省 㗰氣啦 小學雞先絕交"},{"pid":"a055b2d3338dc1e250a714d33bcf79d4761d8935","tid":689642,"uid":91929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 連婆"},{"pid":"6e80d25c3999d7d656d0e4925695d06f1272c0a3","tid":689642,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"絕"},{"pid":"ba18f81b99f6f282dd42f1c2b5fcc4f87c0dc88e","tid":689642,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b33a7bf9ba1719b7a5895acc8c60273679cbfc99","tid":689642,"uid":4876,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"負評係俾你 投你老母閪"},{"pid":"0e40797703999e9dcb1bdb201f958b435769008e","tid":689642,"uid":91929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a055b2d3338dc1e250a714d33bcf79d4761d8935","tid":689642,"uid":91929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 連婆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"咁仲要上網問，食屎啦你"}]}